item.title: CVE-2023-46651|2023-10-25T13:54:40.143Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20warnings%20plugin
item.description: Jenkins Warnings Plugin 10.5.0 and earlier does not set the appropriate context for credentials lookup, allowing attackers with Item/Configure permission to access and capture credentials they are not entitled to. This fix has been backported to 10.4.1.
